reviewText: I really can't say that I don't like it.  The reason that I sent this back was mainly because, the description was not clear and I thought that I was ordering a DVD about a the actual painting, the "Seven Sins", not a musical composition based upon the work of art itself.  So, it's not that I don't like it, the description was not very clear, and the fact of the matter is that, I just didn't want it.  It is not what I thought I was ordering.
